  <tr> <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="bodycontent" --> 
    <td id="maintext"><div id="cptitle">About Cal Parents</div>
      <!-- closing div for id="cptitle" -->
      <h3>To Our Cal Parents</h3>
      <p>On behalf of our faculty and staff, welcome to Cal! I hope you will use 
        this parents web site intensively and often &#8212; it will point you 
        to a dazzling array of resources, news, events, programs, and opportunities 
        at UC Berkeley.</p>
      <p>As parents, you've played a special role in your student's 
        success &#8212; and earning admission to Berkeley is no small success. 
        Simply put, Berkeley is the best public teaching and research university 
        in the nation. Our students find their experience here exciting and energizing, 
        as they navigate the frontiers of knowledge with some of the top scholars 
        in the nation. I hope you will follow their educational journey here and 
        share in the excitement of this remarkable campus.</p>
      <p>Your students will find help at Berkeley if they ask &#8212; encourage 
        them to seek out professors, get to know staff members, and look for opportunities 
        to meet new friends, whether in living groups, classes, or campus activities 
        of every stripe. They are guided by a dedicated faculty and staff, but 
        they also learn from each other, peers with a phenomenal range of backgrounds 
        and interests. </p>
      <p>All of us at Berkeley are proud of our students and our campus. But don't 
        take my word for it &#8212; <a href="/visiting/index.shtml">visit</a> 
        campus often, <a href="/about/dates.shtml">attend events</a>, 
        read up on <a href="/campusnews/index.shtml">campus news</a>, 
        and explore the <a href="http://www.berkeley.edu">web</a>. As I meet many 
        of you in the coming years, I hope to find that you, like your children, 
        are making the most of this special place.</p>
      <p>Robert J. Birgeneau<br>
        Chancellor</p>
      <!-- closing div for class="hilite" -->
      <h4>Related links</h4>
      <ul class="blue">
